1. Imam *traku* za kosu u torbi. (I have a hairband in my bag.)
2. Oni su *zalepili traku* na pokvareni kabl. (They taped the broken cable with tape.)
3. Našao sam staru *traku* sa snimkom moje mature. (I found an old tape with a recording of my graduation.)
4. Nije dobro kada se nešto veže samo *trakom*. (It's not good when something is only tied with a ribbon.)
5. *Traka* za trčanje je omiljeni spravni u teretani. (Treadmill is a favorite equipment in the gym.)
6. Devojka je *umotala traku* oko poklona. (The girl wrapped a ribbon around the gift.)
7. Kupio sam novu *trakastu testeru* za drvo. (I bought a new bandsaw for wood.)
8. Ova *traka asfalta* je nova, postavljena je juče. (This strip of asphalt is new, it was laid yesterday.)
9. Njihov bend izdao je novu *traku*. (Their band released a new tape.)
10. Rekla mi je da mi šalje *traku* snimka na mejl. (She told me she'll send me the recording file via email.)